column3: “This strain is a great head high and it smells...a lot. The taste is also very different than what I’m used to and it takes an acquired taste. I’m a constant smoker so I tend to smoke a lot throughout the day, and this strain makes me incredibly sleepy after awhile.”
“This is a very interesting strain. It’s pretty funky in aroma and the high is pretty invigorating. I enjoyed this strain throughout the day and didn’t feel the sleepiness in my experience.”
